Name: Average time from SW-Checklist Completed to SW-Awaiting AE Assignment
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'SW-Checklist Completed' and activity 'SW-Awaiting AE Assignment'

Name: Total time between SW-Checklist Completed and SW-Awaiting AE Assignment across all cases
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'SW-Checklist Completed' and activity 'SW-Awaiting AE Assignment'

Name: Minimum time it takes for SW-Awaiting AE Assignment to occur after SW-Checklist Completed
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'SW-Checklist Completed' and activity 'SW-Awaiting AE Assignment'

Name: Average duration of the SW-Awaiting AE Assignment activity itself (time until the next activity starts)
Metric: The average of the duration between activity SW-Awaiting AE Assignment and the end of the case

Name: Average time from SW-Awaiting AE Assignment to SW-Initial Reviewer Selection in variants leading to SW-EIC Reject
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'SW-Awaiting AE Assignment' and activity 'SW-Initial Reviewer Selection'

Name: Total time from SW-Awaiting AE Assignment to SW-AE Assign Reviewers in cases where reviewer assignment required multiple attempts
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'SW-Awaiting AE Assignment' and activity 'SW-AE Assign Reviewers'

Name: Time from SW-Awaiting AE Assignment to SW-Awaiting EIC Decision in variants that passed through SW-Reviewer Agreed at least once
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'SW-Awaiting AE Assignment' and activity 'SW-Awaiting EIC Decision'

Name: Average time it takes SW-Awaiting AE Assignment to be followed by any reviewer-related activity (e.g., SW-Initial Reviewer Selection, SW-AE Assign Reviewers)
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'SW-Awaiting AE Assignment' and activity 'SW-Initial Reviewer Selection'

Name: Elapsed time between SW-Awaiting AE Assignment and the first occurrence of SW-Reviewer Agreed in the same case
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'SW-Awaiting AE Assignment' and activity 'SW-Reviewer Agreed'

Name: Total resolution time of SW-Awaiting AE Assignment in cases that eventually resulted in SW-EIC Accept
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'SW-Awaiting AE Assignment' and the end of case where activity 'SW-EIC Accept occurs

Name: Minimum time from SW-Awaiting AE Assignment to SW-Reviewer Agreed in variants with no reviewer decline events
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'SW-Awaiting AE Assignment' and activity 'SW-Reviewer Agreed'

Name: Time of SW-Awaiting AE Assignment cycle measured as the interval between its start and the start of the subsequent activity in the ACM journal review process
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity SW-Awaiting AE Assignment and the end of the case

Name: Minimum time between SW-Awaiting AE Assignment and SW-Initial Reviewer Selection in high-performance variants (performance < 200000)
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'SW-Awaiting AE Assignment' and activity 'SW-Initial Reviewer Selection'

Name: Total waiting time to SW-Awaiting AE Assignment grouped by case:concept:name
Metric: ERROR: computing metric {'begin': activity == 'SW-Awaiting AE Assignment'", 'end': '', 'aggregation': 'total', 'group_by': 'concept:name'}"
